{"tid":1225804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛夢絲夢遊仙境］生存指南·危險裝備篇","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T09:17:52.000Z","uid":146736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4eee6f8193032ff5610af5a65b39d7e12f5a3c4","tid":1225804,"uid":146736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最近發夢發現個仙境多左好多鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不段叫人用磚呀火呀個啲野<br />\n大家要保持冷靜 點都唔好用 <br />\n唔係就會比位人入 比更多嘅人話我地係暴徒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝備簡述如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來歷不明的磚同鐵枝：<br />\n用左就會有位比人話我地係暴徒！<br />\n同埋拋左過去仲會變成敵方武器 增加對方武器添！<br />\n真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n火：<br />\n熊熊烈火 你估咁容易控制咩<br />\n萬一唔好彩 燒埋自己友呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據狗狗記者會嘅講法<br />\n玩火仲有可能會令到佢地用實彈添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未用過嘅嘢(如：漆彈）：<br />\n由工具精靈提供嘅神奇小鼠工具真係咪用呀<br />\n可能殺傷力唔大 但係都有機比狗話我地行動升級<br />\n大家都知 最近仙境瘋狗症爆發 佢地都跟埋升級 <br />\n後果真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 只想大家係仙境減少啲未知嘅威脅<br />\n同唔好比位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nBtw 暫緩不等於撤銷 6.16 上街見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"31cab176e8983e3796e8d7fb1a843e3f498331ba","tid":1225804,"uid":146736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:49:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"874f3f6852f7a388813bda568fa12505ee5f4814","tid":1225804,"uid":146736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc07e21a53b